===RKK Tag Team Championship===
The '''RKK Tag Team Championship''' was a [[professional wrestling]] [[tag team]] [[professional wrestling championship|championship]] in the Ring Ka King [[Professional wrestling promotion|promotion]]. RKK hosted a tournament to crown the first champions.

